metadata.name: IlluminatiNFT Summer Solstice: Dawn of Eris 2022
metadata.description: IlluminatiNFT is proud to present Summer Solstice: The Dawn of Eris, a summer-solstice-themed immersive experience celebrating the rebirth of the goddess of discord. Eris brings light, creativity, and reinvention to the NFT space through the devotion of her followers. Join us on this day of celebration, together we will harness the power of the sun to be truly illuminated. Tonight, we are fully awake. Tomorrow, we recede back into the shadows, keeping our secrets hidden once again.
